{
  "texts": [
    "When looking at the overall system performance, GT consistently performs well across all languages and metrics, often outperforming the other systems; GPT-4 shows competitive performance but generally falls short of GT's performance, especially in BLEU, chrF2, and TER scores.",
    "Vicuna underperforms significantly compared to GT in all languages and metrics.",
    "Its performance is also lower than GPT-4 across all comparisons.",
    "According to AEMs, fifteen out of sixteen best scores are obtained by GT (BLEU in Brazilian Portuguese, chrF3 in Turkish and COMET in Turkish).",
    "The remaining best score is achieved by GPT-4 (TER in Brazilian Portuguese)."
  ]
}